data.description: This Florida gem in Sunset Lakes offers the perfect blend of comfort and luxury living in an established gated community with low HOA fees. This single-story home is ideal for families, featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The 2-car garage with epoxy floors not only adds a touch of luxury but also provides convenient attic stairs leading to over 200 square feet of additional storage. One of the standout features of this property is the cutting-edge theater room, creating an ideal space for movie nights and gatherings. The home's design follows an ''Urban Chic'' aesthetic, complete with an open floor plan, tall ceilings, and ceramic tile flooring throughout the common areas. The kitchen is a highlight, boasting Epicurean features, solid wood cabinets, granite countertops, and BOSCH stainless-steel appliances, making it a chef's dream. The bathrooms have been tastefully updated with new lighting, fixtures, and vanities. The spacious owner's suite is a private retreat with an en suite bathroom featuring an oversized shower, dual vanities, and a large walk-in closet. Bedrooms 2 and 3 are generously sized with high ceilings and offer walk-in closets with built-in storage. The exterior of the home was freshly painted in 2022, and new gutters and hurricane shutters were installed for added protection. The saltwater swimming pool provides a relaxing oasis in your own backyard, perfect for enjoying the Florida summers. With its convenient location near major highways, a short drive to the beaches, and the port, this property allows you to make the most of what the Space Coast has to offer. Boasting over 2500 square feet of space, this home has been meticulously upgraded and maintained, ensuring it's move-in ready. Don't miss the opportunity to schedule a tour and experience this secluded retreat for yourself, where you can begin building cherished memories in your new pool home.
